::Primal Prime::

    Prime sighed as he headed out of the base. Hot Rod still was battle 
oriented. It might be a problem. But Prime's first concern was the Matrix. He 
was going to need it to stop Unicron. Just as he got out side he senses that 
more comrades had arrived on the planet.
    "Ultra Magnus?" He said to himself.
